revision.text:
{{Primary sources|date=January 2009}}[[Image:Coca museum.jpg|thumb|The Coca Museum, Bolivia.]]
The '''Coca Museum''' (in [[Spanish language|Spanish]], '''Museo de la Coca''') covers the history of the [[coca]] plant from the [[Andes|Andean]] region and related drug [[cocaine]].<ref>http://www.lonelyplanet.com/bolivia/la-paz/sights/museums-galleries/coca-museum</ref> It is associated with the International Coca Research Institute (ICORI) in [[La Paz]], the capital of [[Bolivia]]. A travelling version of the museum is available.
